summary: Just a character i made with Enhanced Character Edit
descriptionHtml:
♫♫REQUIREMENTS♫♫ 

Enhanced Character Edit: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?

Any UNP body

Skimpy Armour and Clothing Replacer: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57657/?

Fair Skin Complexion: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?


♫♫INSTALLATION♫♫
Put the CME save in C:\Users\[name]\Documents\My Games\skyrim\CME_save then put the .skse in C:\Users\[name]\Documents\My Games\skyrim\saves
then go into the game and load it up and you should be done!
